Silakan, cobalah.

00:29:28.869 --> 00:29:31.271
Tolong, berhenti.

00:29:33.307 --> 00:29:35.709
Siapa yang memukuli wanita sebrutal itu?

00:29:35.709 --> 00:29:36.510
Apa?

