Tidak, Gi Myung.

00:30:10.711 --> 00:30:11.778
Sakit...

00:30:11.778 --> 00:30:13.046
memberimu uang.

00:30:13.046 --> 00:30:15.782
Jadi tolong berhenti mengganggu Rosanna.

